                    <h2>Publications</h2>
                    <div class="line"></div>
                    <div class="articleBody clear">
                        <p>Bibliography on 
                            <a href="http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/indices/a-tree/s/Simons:Joseph_A=.html">DBLP</a>.
